     <l n="1" met="-+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="11">a frail Thing is Beauty, says Baron ,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="11">Perceiving his Mistress had one Eye of Glass:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-" line_length="7">And scarcely had He ;</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="11">When She more confus'd, as more angry She grew,</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="11">By a negligent Rage prov'd the Maxim too true:</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-" line_length="7">She dropt the Eye, and .</l>
